caption.body: An aspiring writer is forced to question his understanding of the world when he sees what he thinks is a UFO and meets Stevie, a fellow high school student with peculiar insight, in Austin S. Harris’ thesis film for NYU’s Tisch School of the Arts.  See "Stevie’s Aliens" by Austin S. Harris (@austinsharris), now playing in the Video Arts Room located pre-security in the International Terminal. http://bit.ly/2HRU35n
